missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: With the aide of our Sullustan allies we have formed a plan for putting an end to Imperial aggression in this sector. Disguised as an Imperial Shuttle we are going to place a bomb in the Invincible's hangar bay. To do this we need to capture design staff from the Cygnus Corporation to help us modify one of our shuttles to Imperial specifications. Red Squadron will provide cover while Gold Squadron jumps in to disable the Cygnus shuttles, before our boarding craft jump in. Good luck.
Red Squadron head to the jump point immediately.
Looks like they're testing a new model of fighter. Their identification beacon is reading X-G1 Star Wing.
Those Star Wings are heading straight for us. Red Squadron break formation and engage.
This is Gold Leader. The shuttles have been disabled. Activating beacon for boarding craft.
This is Capture One. The target is marked and we're moving to engage.
It took a little persuading, but the Cygnus staff have kindly joined us on board. Moving to jump point.
The boarding craft have safely jumped.
There are still fighters active. Clear them out so we can safely make the jump to Hyperspace.
Okay Red Squadron. Head to the jump point.
Looks like that Super Freighter has teeth. Detecting four Tie Fighters launching.
Another group of Tie Fighters are launching!
Looks like they've had enough. The Super Freighter is preparing to jump.
See you back at the rendezvous Red One.
